                <html:p>Lower bounds are defined similarly: a <html:dfn>Lower Bound</html:dfn> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \in  S]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \leq  x]]></fr:tex> for every <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  E]]></fr:tex>, and we say <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> is <html:dfn>Bounded Below</html:dfn>.</html:p>
